(function($){$.fn.animated=function(inEffect,outEffect){$(this).css("visibility","hidden").addClass("animated").waypoint(function(dir){if(dir==="down"){$(this).removeClass(outEffect).addClass(inEffect).css("visibility","visible");}else{$(this).removeClass(inEffect).addClass(outEffect).css("visibility","visible");};},{offset:"100%"}).waypoint(function(dir){if(dir==="down"){$(this).removeClass(inEffect).addClass(outEffect).css("visibility","visible");}else{$(this).removeClass(outEffect).addClass(inEffect).css("visibility","visible");};},{offset:-$(window).height()});};})(jQuery);